"PvP"], "long_description": "Step into the adrenaline-pumping world of Paintball Playground VR, where you can unleash your competitive spirit and tactical skills in a virtual battleground like never before. Get ready to dive into heart-pounding paintball matches that will test your aim, strategy, and teamwork in a dynamic and immersive VR environment.\n\nKey Features\n\n1. Realistic paintball physics - Paintball Playground VR offers realistic paintball physics, including accurate ball trajectory, impact, and splatter effects, enhancing the immersive gameplay experience.\n\n2. Variety of Game Modes - Choose from a variety of game modes, including classic speedball, team deathmatch, and 1v1, each offering unique challenges and opportunities for strategic gameplay.\n\n3. Customizable Gear -  Paintball Playground VR offers extensive customization options for players to personalize their gear and weapons, allowing for unique identity and play style.\n\n4. Multiplayer - The game supports competitive multiplayer modes, where players can team up with friends or compete against others in intense paintball matches, fostering teamwork, communication, and strategic gameplay.\n\n5. Dynamic Environments - The game features a variety of meticulously designed maps with different layouts, terrains, and obstacles to provide dynamic and challenging gameplay for players.\n", "short_description": "A Sports/Shooter game where you compete against other players on SpeedBall, SpeedQB or Woodsball maps."}]}, "developer_name": "Triangle's Workshop", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://xsolla.com/privacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Triangle's Workshop", "support_website_url": "https://paintball-playground-vr.xsollasitebuilder.com/", "website_url": "https://paintball-playground-vr.xsollasitebuilder.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category":